      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINSOME JET (1) was a winner two back then strongly fancied last time but could only manage a second (29.77) at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Makes plenty of appeal. CUMBRIA JACK (3) is in hot form with back to back wins at this track, running a scintillating 29.38 two back following up with 29.71 last time. Flying and looks a key chance again. BACK TOMORROW (2) is a handy type who notched her 19th career success when too good (29.65) from Box 2 at this track. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and three minor placings from six starts. Can make it two on the bounce. OFF THE CHART (6) is building a solid run wins and will play a big role again.",
